name: Crossword Hoodie
description:
This digital version of the Crossword Hoodie comes with its physical one. 
Every Skele consumer that will buy this hoodie physically will receive this NFT gifted to their wallet. 

The number of editions is in exact correlation with the quantity of hoodies that were crafted in Montpellier, France. 

Garment collection initially dropped on 11/05/2021

www.skele.rip
